---
import Layout from "@layouts/PageLayout.astro";
import Listening from "@assets/images/listening.svg";
import Creativity from "@assets/images/creativity.svg";
import Hero from "@assets/images/hero.svg";

const meta = {
  title: "AudioBooks",
  description: "Audiobooks app",
};
---

<Layout {meta}>
  <section class="p-12 md:mt-[76px]">
    <div class="mx-auto text-center max-w-screen-lg md:pb-16 pb-10">
      <h1
        class="mb-4 text-4xl font-bold leading-none tracking-tight text-gray-900 md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl dark:text-white"
      >
        AudioBooks
      </h1>
      <p class="text-muted text-xl dark:text-slate-300 mb-6">Listen to all the good stuff</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto text-center max-w-screen-lg md:pb-16 pb-10">
      <p class="text-muted text-xl dark:text-slate-300 mb-6">
        Best-selling audiobooks, exclusive originals, popular podcasts, and
        more. Always find the best of what you're into. Listen on your phone or
        tablet, or download for later.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="m-auto max-w-5xl">
      <img src={Listening} alt="listening" class="m-auto" />
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="dark:bg-slate-800 bg-blue-50">
    <div
      class="font-medium px-4 max-w-6xl mx-auto py-4 sm:px-6 text-center text-md"
    >
      Best in the universe (said no one ever)
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="mx-auto px-10 sm:px-6 max-w-6xl lg:px-8 lg:py-20 py-16">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 row-gap-10">
      <div class="md:basis-1/2 md:mt-0 mt-10">
        <div class="dark:text-slate-400 text-lg mb-12">
          <h3
            class="font-bold dark:text-white text-2xl mb-2 sm:text-3xl tracking-tight"
          >
            Why choose us?
          </h3>
          Our audiobook app is the perfect solution for book lovers on the go. 
          With a vast library of titles to choose from, users can easily download and listen to their favorite books whenever and wherever they want. 
          The app features a user-friendly interface and allows users to customize their listening experience with adjustable playback speed and sleep timer. 
          Additionally, users can create their own personal reading lists and pick up where they left off with automatic bookmarking. 
          Whether commuting, exercising, or simply relaxing, our audiobook app makes it easy to enjoy a great book.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:basis-1/2 md:mt-0 mt-10">
        <img src={Creativity} alt="creativity" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="dark:bg-slate-800 bg-blue-50 pt-10 pb-10 px-10">
    <div class="lg:max-w-2xl max-w-xl sm:mx-auto md:basis-1">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl md:mx-auto mb-10 md:mb-12">
        <p
          class="text-primary dark:text-blue-200 font-semibold text-base tracking-wide uppercase"
        >
          You may ask yourself
        </p>
        <h2
          class="font-bold font-heading mb-4 leading-tighter tracking-tighter text-4xl md:text-5xl"
        >
          Why even bother with books?
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 row-gap-10">
      <div class="md:basis-1/2 md:mt-0 mt-10 ml-auto mr-10">
        <img src={Hero} alt="hero" />
      </div>
      <div class="md:basis-1/2 md:mt-0 mt-10">
        <div class="dark:text-slate-400 text-lg mb-12 max-w-xl text-justify">
          <h3
            class="font-bold dark:text-white text-2xl mb-2 sm:text-3xl tracking-tight"
          >
            The answer is simple
          </h3>
          Listening to audiobooks can offer a variety of benefits for both personal and professional development. Some of the benefits include:
          Improved concentration and focus: As you listen to an audiobook, you are actively engaging with the story and the narrator's voice, which can help to improve focus and concentration.
          Increased vocabulary and comprehension: Listening to audiobooks can expose you to new words and phrases, helping to expand your vocabulary and improve comprehension.
          Increased imagination and visualization: Listening to audiobooks allows you to create mental images of the story, characters, and settings, which can help to improve imagination and visualization.
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
